name: BAKERY
description:
Each mirror is handmade using quality solid wood and then sanded, distressed and stained to bring out the natural grain, making each one unique. A matt black vinyl graphic is then applied to the face of the mirror. There will be two D-rings attached on the rear for easy hanging. Overall size: 480mm x 635mm Mirror size: 295mm x 445mm Frame width: 95mm Frame thickness: 21mm Please note as each item is handmade, no two are alike and may vary slightly in colour and markings. Please allow up to 10 working days for delivery.
Fancy something a little more personal? Please see 'Bespoke Designs' for more information.
